<item>
            <title>[LU-7928] Wrong params for mdd_declare_rename at mdd_rename</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7928</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;mdd_rename call mdd_declare_rename and pass lsname ltnam this way&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;        rc = mdd_declare_rename(env, mdd, mdd_spobj, mdd_tpobj, mdd_sobj,
                                mdd_tobj, lsname, ltname, ma, ldata, handle);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;but mdd_declare_rename use those in different order&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;static int mdd_declare_rename(const struct lu_env *env,                                                             
                              struct mdd_device *mdd,
                              struct mdd_object *mdd_spobj,                                                         
                              struct mdd_object *mdd_tpobj,                                                         
                              struct mdd_object *mdd_sobj,                                                          
                              struct mdd_object *mdd_tobj,                                                          
                              const struct lu_name *sname,                                                          
                              const struct lu_name *tname,                                                          
                              struct md_attr *ma,
                              struct linkea_data *ldata,                                                            
                              struct thandle *handle)  
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
